  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Provide Clean Water in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water is a fundamental human need. Each person on Earth requires at least 20 to 50 litres of clean, safe water a day for drinking, cooking, and simply keeping themselves clean.There is a crisis of access to safe and clean water in villages where Sprout Care Foundation operate. The water sources that exist are often severely contaminated with dirt, bacteria and bugs and the people must share the spring with animals. This results into severe illness and premature death as part of everyday life.</narrative>
  </description>
